  "description": "<i>Helvera: Mistress of the Park</i> is a fantasy text adventure.<br><br>The player starts the game locked in a dark and dingy cell that was carved from a single block of stone. From here they must find a way, not only to escape but also to restore an altar and lift the 'Curse Of Darkness'.<br><br>This game was developed using <i>Professional Adventure Writer</i>. It supports the standard shortcuts such as N/S/E/W for North/South/East/West. However this does mean that when the player is asked a 'Yes/No' question they must respond 'NO' in full. <br>The game can be saved which is important as the player can expect to die.\n",
